    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "My idea is to simply add a channel state called `GRPC_CHANNEL_BAD_SUBCHANNELS` as a signal from the LB policies to ask the client channel to help request a re-resolution. This is very similar to how `GRPC_CHANNEL_SHUTDOWN` is interpreted now.\r\n\r\nPlease let me know if this method is insufficient."
